version_description: These are the chords for 'Dangerous Game,' rather than the tab.
3 doors down - Fell From the Moon -Capo 5 - Link https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_AHOi9xEnIY.

This version is different due to a few chords being changed around from other versions you may find. Most notably, the F chord has been switched to an Fmaj7. Also, several different riffs have been written out for ease of use. This tab was designed to be relatively easy but still retain the quality sound of the actual song.
